{
  "stem": "597.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Korets itself was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Korets himself was a town-- a Jewish town, a very-- a very nice town-- a Jewish town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people was working people, a few business people, and a few-- and working people-- hard-working people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wasn't afraid for work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the problem is, they didn't have where work-- a lot of unemployment there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People would go around doing things what they didn't supposed to do-- as long as can-- you can make a dollar, you can make a-- to-- to make a living.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- they saw some of-- poor people, but very nice people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them rich-- not very few-- a couple. 73% of population was Jewish-- Korets-- the rest was gentile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the gentile, they live around the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The city was a-- we had a lot of synagogues-- 17 synagogues.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One big one was built by the-- by the-- by a [NON-ENGLISH]-- Polish nobleman-- [NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He build only the-- he build three-- three-- not synagogues-- one synagogue and two churches-- one Polish-Catholic and one-- and-- the other one was not Catholic-- it was orthodox.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For each-- each nationality, he build up a church-- a house of worship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all of them was impacted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is a-- the-- the Greek orthodox churches, like our-- now museum, because it's so long-- it stays there now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Jewish synagogue is-- is-- is broken-- burned down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the-- the Greek orthodox church is still there-- and a monastery near there, with the nuns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is like a-- I was-- I got a letter from Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a-- a stamp with this-- with this church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like a-- like a museum now, because it's old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a whole thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they put upon a stamp.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
